15. Service

Exposes pods internally/externally.

Types:

ClusterIP
NodePort
LoadBalancer
16. ClusterIP

Internal communication inside cluster.

Default service type.

17. NodePort

Exposes app using node IP + port.

18. LoadBalancer

Creates external cloud load balancer.

Used in AWS/Azure/GCP.

19. Ingress

Manages HTTP/HTTPS routing.

Example:

domain.com → application
